node.text: On this episode of Are We Blair Yet?, Onion Travel vlogger Blair Ryleigh shows you how to eat on the cheap in Los Angeles by digging through the dumpsters behind some of the city's hottest restaurants.

node.title: How To Find The Best Cheap Eats – With @HotelsDotCom
